attributes.title: Jack Morten with a Snake
attributes.description:
They caught and killed a snake in the barracks. This is Jack Morten with the dead snake.

Editor's Comment:
Pte. 2393 John Clarke Morten, 1/7th Bn. Manchester Regiment, was commissioned Second Lieutenant and later attached to the Royal Air Force.
